                <p/>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Philon fils d'Annikeris a consacré l'autel de marbre.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Philon son of Annikeris dedicated the marble altar.</p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Philon figlio di Annikeris ha dedicato l'altare di marmo.</p>
            </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>Philo's dedication consisted in remodeling the older limestone altar with white marble (see also <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr018000</ref>).</p>
	<p/>
	<p/>
            </div></body>
